data.title: Wing (Military Aviation Unit)
data.meta_description: aac ww2 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides an introduction and overview for the book "Air Force Combat Units of World War II". It summarizes that the book traces the lineage and histories of US Army Air Forces and US Air Force combat units from their origins through 1956. It provides brief histories of each unit, including their assignments, locations, aircraft, commanders, and decorations. The book serves as an important reference for historians, researchers, and Air Force members to understand the heritage and histories of combat units during World War II and beyond.
